    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an automotive specimen of exceptional caliber, maintained to the highest standards of preservation. This vehicle exhibits an impeccable exterior finish and a pristine, showroom-quality interior, reflecting a history of fastidious ownership. Every mechanical system operates with the exactitude intended by its original engineering. We invite the most discerning buyers to inspect this investment-grade vehicle, which stands as a definitive testament to uncompromising quality and aesthetic integrity.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
