    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so sad to let this absolute gem go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in incredible shape\u2014seriously, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept in a garage, and treated like a member of the family. You won't find a single scratch or hiccup here. If you're looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you! Come take a look, you're going to fall in love!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant. This specimen exhibits flawless compression across all six cylinders and has undergone a comprehensive preventative maintenance overhaul, including VAC Motorsports rod bearings and a structural subframe reinforcement. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission delivers crisp engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for optimal torque vectoring. Suspension geometry remains precise with fresh bushings and OEM-spec dampers. The exterior retains its factory depth with zero paint meter variance, while the interior remains a time capsule. Mechanically turn-key and aesthetically peerless.",
